        protected abstract boolean render(android.graphics.Canvas canvas)
        パラメータ:
        canvas - Canvas to draw.
        戻り値:
        true to end drawing. No more called in next update. If redrawing is required, call invalidate(). false to continues draw. This behavior can be modified overriding isDirty().
